    <title>Proposing an amendment to the Constitution of the United States to prohibit the President from making recess appointments.</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDate>2016-07-05</actionDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-04-24T14:38:54Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2016-07-05T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Constitutional Amendment </strong></p> <p>This joint resolution proposes a constitutional amendment prohibiting the President from filling any vacancy during the recess of the Senate.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
    </summaries>
